monster-rpg2 (1.11.0-1ubuntu1) maverick; urgency=low

  * Smaller file size for quicker downloads
  * High quality music can still be downloaded at users leisure for free from
    within the game and will play automatically when the download finishes 
  * All new player battle sprites 
  * All new item icons 
  * Preserve aspect ratio mode that fills as much of the screen as it can
    while preserving aspect 
  * Change filtering modes without restarting the game 
  * Massive scripting and area editing overhaul to make NPCs face you when
    you talk to them and make high walls "above" the player 
  * Dozens of other tweaks and fixes to improve the look and flow of the game
 
 -- Trent Gamblin <trent@nooskewl.com>  Sun, 3 Jun 2012 08:37:00 -0700

